		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">陆巡舰使用攻坚锯进行两次来回挥锯，依次造成<span color="#ff9999">50%,60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="767" width="442" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于陆巡舰后方时，陆巡迅速使用攻坚锯挥舞一圈，造成1-2次<span color="#ff9999">60%</span><span>伤害，随后起飞并转身面朝玩家，缓缓落地，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1055" width="428" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">自身存在「高热」计量条，满计量<span color="#ffdfbf">600</span><span>点。陆巡舰在受到</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>攻击后，将积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">5</span><span>高热，每额外n单位火元素额外积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">5n</span><span>高热，计量过半后进入「红温过载」状态，计量满后进行「降控温御」，持续减少高热计量。<br/>本高热计量不受</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span>影响。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/超重型陆巡舰%B7机动战垒.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/超重型陆巡舰%B7机动战垒.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="681">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/超重型陆巡舰%B7机动战垒.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1391" y="969">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">交替进行下列两种攻击：<br/>陆巡舰使用舰炮轰击，造成<span color="#99ffff">70%</span><span>伤害；<br/>陆巡舰使用攻坚锯进行一次挥锯，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1055" width="440" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">未成功击破护罩时，陆巡舰升空，利用舰炮轰击，造成<span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害并留下冰地面；随后利用攻坚锯下劈重重坠落，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">150%</span><span>伤害；落地后持续切锯造成</span><span color="#ff9999">25%</span><span>伤害；坠落时将冰地面替换为持续12s的火地面，并持续造成</span><span color="#ff9999">6%</span><span>伤害；升空与坠落伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">闪避帧均无法躲避</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1128" width="441" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">深渊抗性：正常150%，红温过载状态50%，瘫痪为-20%。<br/>高热：满计量600点。受到<span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>攻击后，积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.833%</span><span>(5)高热，每额外1U火元素量积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.833%</span><span>(5)高热，计量过半后进入「红温过载」状态，计量满后进行「降控温御」。<br/>散热套件：</span><span color="#99ffff">28冻</span><span>盾，持续18s，存在期间将持续减少高热计量条，击破后瘫痪16s，填满热量，全抗下降，恢复后清空热量。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
