		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于较远的位置时，陆巡舰起飞并缓缓降落至预警位置，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
